{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6bb851df19","title":"樊执中同志关於合川南坪公社干部违法乱纪情况的一些反映","origin":"四川省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9ca3965c26","index":0,"year":1960,"month":11,"day":13,"articleId":"6bb851df19"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"91ceb9f85a","type":"title","text":"樊执中同志关于合川南坪公社干部违法乱纪情况的一些反映","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6bb851df19"},{"id":"135dab9843","type":"paragraph","text":"一、在该社已伤亡的496人中，属于吊死、逼死、活埋的有42人；属于打残、打伤的有62人；属于因病但不少是强迫劳动、扣饭（一天三两）致死的有392人。这些非正常的伤亡大都是公社党委书记亲自主持下命令所造成的。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6bb851df19"},{"id":"9a0001fda8","type":"paragraph","text":"二、该社被罚款的有387户，罚款22400元；发生拦路抢劫的也有16起。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6bb851df19"},{"id":"799adb7f25","type":"appellation","text":"以上问题，现正继续深入的搞下去，可能在20日结束，对这个问题群众普遍反映“这是第二次解放”（土改是第一次解放）。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6bb851df19"},{"id":"6def76f340","type":"paragraph","text":" 十一月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6bb851df19"},{"id":"4c470699f2","type":"paragraph","text":"抄送各书记、秘书长，监委，公安厅分党组。  （16分）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6bb851df19"},{"id":"ca7a97fde1","type":"paragraph","text":"中共四川省委办公厅秘书处  一九六○年十一月十四日抄","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6bb851df19"}],"page":{"id":"e7fef1c983","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"6bb851df19","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}